Titolo: Xeno Crisis

Anno: 2019

Descrizione: Xeno Crisis is a 2019 homebrew twin-stick shooter developed by indie game studio Bitmap Bureau for the Sega Mega Drive, with releases for the Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, PlayStation Vita, Xbox One, Microsoft Windows, macOS, Linux, Sega Dreamcast, Evercade, and Neo Geo. The game was fully funded on Kickstarter on January 10, 2018, with a release on October 28, 2019.

Genere: Shooter 

Valutazione: 74
